    <name>Passo del Mortirolo (Italy)</name>
    <desc>Italy · 12.4 km · +1300 m · 10.5% avg. Brutally steep and narrow from Mazzo di Valtellina; ramps over 18% made it a Pantani legend. Approximate geometry anchored at the real trailhead for indoor training, not the exact road.</desc>
